Y9JJ.title: The Beginning.
Y9JJ.content: You awake on a Desert island. What do you do?

4WPO.title: You weren't able to find any food

DV25.title: You weren't able to start a fire

71F4.title: You weren't able to kill yourself

U5EM.title: You came all over yourself
U5EM.content: You made a big ol mess. What now?

8SPQ.title: You can't get over the jewish women
8SPQ.content: Theres just too many great ones out there! You MUST find one...

0L1M.title: You are happy
0L1M.content: Those pants made you soo happy. But they start dancing in your stomach! What do you do?

WIQA.title: You took pants out of stomach
WIQA.content: There are now dirty pants in your hands.

SOP7.title: You put the pants on
SOP7.content: You gained the power of dance!

NCNL.title: They like you
NCNL.content: Your pants dance is cool. They make you a bowl of chicken soup.
